{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/hira-dazzle-kenalkan-anggota-baru-dan-single-original/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Hira Dazzle Kenalkan Anggota Baru dan Single Original","content":"\n<p>Telah eksis sejak tahun 2015, grup cover dance Hira Dazzle siap memulai chapter terbaru dalam karir mereka. Pada acara launching lineup Hira Dazzle tahun 2019 tanggal 28 Juli lalu, mereka tampil dalam lineup yang lebih segar dengan suntikan anggota baru dan tim manajemen baru.</p>\n\n\n\n<iframe width=\"720\" height=\"480\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/E_Ih_xB_440\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n\n\n<p>Dalam acara yang diadakan di Kaskus Playground ini, grup yang beranggotakan inti Richan, Annya, Kimmy dan Ayumi ini melepas satu member yang akan graduate serta menyambut empat anggota baru, yang mana membawa total anggotanya genap delapan orang. </p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"55044\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/hira-dazzle-kenalkan-anggota-baru-dan-single-original/attachment/01-hira-dazzle-2019/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/01-hira-dazzle-2019.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-hira-dazzle-2019\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/01-hira-dazzle-2019-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/01-hira-dazzle-2019.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/01-hira-dazzle-2019.jpg\" alt=\"Penampilan lagu Slihouette dari Hira Dazzle. Sumber: CIAYO Pictures\" class=\"wp-image-55044\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/01-hira-dazzle-2019.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/01-hira-dazzle-2019-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Penampilan lagu Slihouette dari Hira Dazzle. Sumber: CIAYO Pictures</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Acara utama launching Hira Dazzle dimulai dengan cover lagu Silhouette dari Kana-Boon, dan dilanjutkan dengan penampilan lagu original <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Look At Me (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/E_Ih_xB_440\" target=\"_blank\">Look At Me</a>. Di penampilan ini, para member menampilkan keahlian masing-masing mulai dari dansa hingga nyanyian. Dalam penampilannya, mereka mencoba memasukkan muatan lokal seperti koreografi yang terinspirasi tarian tradisional.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Baca Juga: <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/chika-idol-festival-mencari-idol-bertalenta-untuk-ennichisai/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">Chika Idol Festival: Mencari Idol Bertalenta Untuk Ennichisai</a></strong></p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"55045\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/hira-dazzle-kenalkan-anggota-baru-dan-single-original/attachment/02-hira-dazzle-2019/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/02-hira-dazzle-2019.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-hira-dazzle-2019\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/02-hira-dazzle-2019-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/02-hira-dazzle-2019.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/02-hira-dazzle-2019.jpg\" alt=\"Foto bareng setelah ikut game tanya jawab. Sumber: CIAYO Pictures\" class=\"wp-image-55045\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/02-hira-dazzle-2019.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/02-hira-dazzle-2019-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Foto bareng setelah ikut game tanya jawab. Sumber: CIAYO Pictures</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Mereka juga menyempatkan waktunya untuk berbagi pengalaman dan cerita lewat sesi talkshow. Mereka menceritakan berbagai macam kesan-kesan selama berkarir di Hira Dazzle, serta pengalaman bersama sesama anggota lainnya. Interaksi dengan fans terasa sangat cair ketika dibuka sesi games berupa tanya jawab.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"55046\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/hira-dazzle-kenalkan-anggota-baru-dan-single-original/attachment/03-hira-dazzle-2019/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/03-hira-dazzle-2019.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-hira-dazzle-2019\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/03-hira-dazzle-2019-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/03-hira-dazzle-2019.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/03-hira-dazzle-2019.jpg\" alt=\"Para caretaker Hira Dazzle menjelaskan strategi promosi mereka. Sumber: CIAYO Pictures\" class=\"wp-image-55046\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/03-hira-dazzle-2019.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/03-hira-dazzle-2019-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Para caretaker menjelaskan strategi promosi mereka. Sumber: CIAYO Pictures</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Dalam acara yang sama pula, Hira Dazzle memperkenalkan tim manajemen baru yang akan mensupport aktivitas mereka. Zhuge Kamiya selaku salah satu caretaker membeberkan strateginya untuk mempromosikan Richan dan kawan-kawan, diantaranya meluncurkan website serta merchandise kaos. Zhuge juga mendeskripsikan Hira Dazzle sebagai “idol gemstone” dimana para anggotanya punya kepribadian dan karakter menarik yang bisa disimbolkan sebagai berbagai jenis batu mulia.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"55047\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/hira-dazzle-kenalkan-anggota-baru-dan-single-original/attachment/04-hira-dazzle-2019/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/04-hira-dazzle-2019.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-hira-dazzle-2019\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/04-hira-dazzle-2019-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/04-hira-dazzle-2019.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/04-hira-dazzle-2019.jpg\" alt=\"Potong tumpeng untuk meresmikan formasi baru Hira Dazzle. Sumber: CIAYO Pictures\" class=\"wp-image-55047\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/04-hira-dazzle-2019.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/04-hira-dazzle-2019-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Potong tumpeng untuk meresmikan formasi baru. Sumber: CIAYO Pictures</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Acara yang bekerja sama dengan Kaskus dan Komunitas Pecinta\nAnime Jakarta (KOPAJA) ini kemudian ditutup dengan penampilan akustik dari\nunreleased song Hira Dazzle untuk pertama kalinya, dan dilanjutkan dengan acara\npotong tumpeng dan makan bersama. Mengutip pernyataan dari caretaker Zhuge\nKamiya, ia berharap acara ini bisa menjadi titik balik untuk bisa memajukan\nkomunitas idol Jejepangan di Indonesia.</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"8d4cc9ac-1ceb-59d9-bb39-ce5663e451d4"}}}